Mar!

87
00:07:36,231 --> 00:07:39,351
Napokon smo odluili
doi u sunanu Kaliforniju.

88
00:07:40,151 --> 00:07:42,904
Lutali smo...
Tu smo se smjestili...

89
00:07:43,114 --> 00:07:46,233
...kada su iz filmskih studija
poele dolaziti ponude.

90
00:07:46,492 --> 00:07:50,989
Nakon to smo ih sve pregledali,
odluismo usreiti Monumental Pictures.

91
00:07:51,289 --> 00:07:54,741
Lina, ti ga mrzi. Sad mu se opire.
Ne prekidaj tu dobru muziku.

92
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:57,249
Phil, sada ti ulazi.

93
00:07:57,504 --> 00:08:02,046
Sad je vidi. A sad dolazi onaj dio
kada ti, Berte, dobija po vilici.

94
00:08:03,052 --> 00:08:03,916
Rez!

95
00:08:04,135 --> 00:08:06,044
Ne, ne! Ne tako!

96
00:08:06,304 --> 00:08:10,598
Trebao si pasti na ank
da razbije ae! Ponovit emo sve.

97
00:08:10,809 --> 00:08:12,683
Idemo, Bert. Bert!

98
00:08:12,936 --> 00:08:14,976
Sjajno! Ba sjajno!

99
00:08:15,189 --> 00:08:17,146
Nosite ga.

100
00:08:17,358 --> 00:08:21,058
Bit e sve u redu. Ve smo ih
toliko izgubili na ovom snimanju!

101
00:08:21,321 --> 00:08:24,155
Sad u morati satima
traiti novog glumca.

102
00:08:24,365 --> 00:08:26,357
G. Dexter, ja u vam pomoi.

103
00:08:26,617 --> 00:08:29,369
Vi? Vi ste glazbenik.
-Nije bitno.

104
00:08:29,580 --> 00:08:31,370
Ma nemojte? Kako se zovete?

105
00:08:31,622 --> 00:08:34,196
Don Lockwood.
Prijatelji me zovu Donald.

106
00:08:34,459 --> 00:08:37,128
Pametnjakovi, ha?
Pokuat emo.

107
00:08:37,379 --> 00:08:39,170
Dajte mu Bertov kostim.

108
00:08:39,422 --> 00:08:44,001
Upamti, Lockwood, moda nee uspjeti
zamijeniti violinu za harfu.

109
00:08:46,221 --> 00:08:47,300
Kamera!

110
00:08:48,348 --> 00:08:51,053
Phil, ulazi. Sad ga vidi.
To je to.

111
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:53,765
A sad, udari ga po vilici!

112
00:08:55,939 --> 00:08:56,770
Rez!

113
00:08:56,983 --> 00:08:58,441
To je bilo divno!

114
00:09:00,236 --> 00:09:02,359
Imate li jo takvih uloga?

115
00:09:02,614 --> 00:09:03,692
Bezbroj.

116
00:09:08,118 --> 00:09:09,363
U redu.

117
00:09:29,933 --> 00:09:33,219
Sve moje uloge u tim
filmovima bile su otmjene...

118
00:09:33,479 --> 00:09:34,854
...profinjene...

119
00:09:35,105 --> 00:09:36,019
...i uglaene.

120
00:09:38,984 --> 00:09:41,736
Naravno, u svim filmovima...

121
00:09:41,988 --> 00:09:45,439
...Lina mi je, kao i uvijek,
bila nadahnue.

122
00:09:45,658 --> 00:09:47,402
Srdana i od pomoi.

123
00:09:47,744 --> 00:09:49,404
Prava dama.

124
00:09:53,374 --> 00:09:56,744
Gice Lamont, ja sam
Don Lockwood, kaskader.

125
00:09:58,921 --> 00:10:01,543
Bilo bi mi zadovoljstvo
raditi s vama.

126
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:02,997
Don!

127
00:10:03,384 --> 00:10:06,137
Ovo je producent naeg filma,
R.F. Simpson.

128
00:10:06,347 --> 00:10:10,131
Vidio sam svjee snimke sa snimanja,
i odmah upitao Dextera tko je kaskader.

129
00:10:10,393 --> 00:10:14,604
Rekao mi je da ste to sve sami izveli.
Igrat ete s Linom u iduem filmu.

130
00:10:14,855 --> 00:10:17,227
Doite da razgovaramo o novcu.

131
00:10:17,482 --> 00:10:19,226
Hvala, g. Simpson.

132
00:10:23,197 --> 00:10:26,151
Jeste li zauzeti veeras,
gice Lamont?

133
00:10:27,827 --> 00:10:29,286
Ba teta.

134
00:10:29,495 --> 00:10:30,824
Ja sam zauzet.

135
00:10:36,002 --> 00:10:40,166
Otad smo Lina i ja
postali nerazdruivi.

136
00:10:40,506 --> 00:10:44,339
Ali najvanije je to i dalje
ivim pod svojim geslom:

137
00:10:44,886 --> 00:10:46,001
"Dostojanstvo.

138
00:10:46,429 --> 00:10:48,421
Dostojanstvo iznad svega."

139
00:10:50,017 --> 00:10:51,013
Hvala, Done.

140
00:10:51,268 --> 00:10:55,765
Sigurna sam da ete vi i
Lina ui u povijest filma...

141
00:10:56,023 --> 00:11:00,768
...i ovim filmom
Kraljevski lupe.

142
00:11:04,573 --> 00:11:05,902
Sve je snimljeno?

143
00:11:18,379 --> 00:11:20,621
"Veeras svijet je na.
Veeras smo sami."

144
00:11:28,640 --> 00:11:30,051
"Mislim da ujem korake."

145
00:11:43,322 --> 00:11:45,030
Tako je profinjena.

146
00:11:45,283 --> 00:11:47,608
Ja u se ubiti.

147
00:12:13,895 --> 00:12:15,438
SVRETAK

148
00:12:26,742 --> 00:12:30,954
Hvala, dame i gospodo.
Hvala, hvala, hvala.

149
00:12:32,915 --> 00:12:36,119
Vae prihvaanje filma Kraljevski lupe
zaista nas je uzbudilo.

150
00:12:36,377 --> 00:12:40,671
Mi smo ga snimali s uitkom,
nadam se da ste ga vi gledali s uitkom.

151
00:12:43,593 --> 00:12:47,887
Mi filmski glumci ba
ne znamo drati govore.

152
00:12:48,140 --> 00:12:50,465
Mi glumom pokazujemo
svoju zahvalnost.

153
00:13:00,945 --> 00:13:04,065
Pravi hit! Bilo je sjajno!
-Don, Lina, bili ste velianstveni.

154
00:13:04,324 --> 00:13:08,108
Lina je bila sjajna iako je djevojka.
-Hej, o emu se tu radi?

155
00:13:08,370 --> 00:13:12,284
Zato nisam smjela govoriti?
Napokon, to je i moja publika!

156
00:13:12,541 --> 00:13:14,034
Oni iz propagande...

157
00:13:14,251 --> 00:13:17,998
...kau da je bolje da se
samo Don obraa publici.

158
00:13:18,255 --> 00:13:19,084
Zato?

159
00:13:19,297 --> 00:13:22,418
Ti si lijepa. Oni misle
da ti je takav i glas.

160
00:13:22,635 --> 00:13:25,504
Ne smijemo zvijezdu izvri
ruglu pod svaku cijenu.

161
00:13:25,762 --> 00:13:30,009
Nitko nema toliki novac.
-to nedostaje mom glasu?

162
00:13:30,267 --> 00:13:33,221
Jesam li glupa ili to?

163
00:13:33,437 --> 00:13:36,391
Ne, nije to,
nego Don je iskusniji.

164
00:13:36,648 --> 00:13:40,100
Za idui put napii mi govor.
Mogu ga upamtiti.

165
00:13:40,361 --> 00:13:43,481
Zato ne izae odmah i ne
citira getisburki manifest.

166
00:13:43,739 --> 00:13:48,283
to zna ti, glasovirau jedan?
Ti si nitko i nita.

167
00:13:48,536 --> 00:13:52,747
Kako doputa da tako razgovaraju
s tvojom zarunicom, dragi?

168
00:13:52,998 --> 00:13:54,328
Zaru...?

169
00:13:54,792 --> 00:13:58,162
Lina, opet si itala
pogrene filmske asopise.

170
00:13:58,421 --> 00:14:01,588
uj, ne smije vjerovati
sve to izmiljaju...

171
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:03,959
...posebice Dora Bailey.

172
00:14:04,178 --> 00:14:08,176
A sada da razjasnimo:
meu nama nema nita.

173
00:14:08,432 --> 00:14:10,969
Nije nikada nita ni bilo.

174
00:14:11,184 --> 00:14:14,435
Samo zrak.
-Daj, Donnie, ne misli to ozbiljno.

175
00:14:14,688 --> 00:14:16,597
Hajde, kasnimo na primanje.

176
00:14:16,857 --> 00:14:20,475
Idite zasebno da se razrijedi
svjetina. Idemo, draga.

177
00:14:20,694 --> 00:14:23,446
Pa-pa, Donnie!
Vidimo se tamo.

178
00:14:24,782 --> 00:14:25,731
"Donnie!"

179
00:14:26,243 --> 00:14:28,530
to joj je?
Zar ne shvaa obazrivi mig?

180
00:14:28,786 --> 00:14:32,073
Zar ne zna da je neodoljiva?
Sama mi je rekla.

181
00:14:32,331 --> 00:14:35,617
Ne mogu je se rijeiti.
Romansa zbog reklame.

182
00:14:35,877 --> 00:14:38,332
Cijena slave.
Slavan si.

183
00:14:38,588 --> 00:14:40,379
Katkad dobije i po glavi.

184
00:14:40,590 --> 00:14:44,374
Pogledaj me! Ja nisam slavan.
Nisam voljen. Nemam zamak.

185
00:14:44,636 --> 00:14:47,127
Nemam novaca. Imam samo...

186
00:14:47,556 --> 00:14:49,798
to imam?
-Ne znam to.

187
00:14:50,058 --> 00:14:51,636
Moram otii odavde.

188
00:15:00,402 --> 00:15:02,608
Nemoj mi rei.
Probuila se guma.

189
00:15:02,864 --> 00:15:06,029
Ne shvaam. Ve 6 sati nisam
imao kvar na tom autu.

190
00:15:06,241 --> 00:15:07,902
Gledajte!
To je Don Lockwood!

191
00:15:08,702 --> 00:15:10,031
Hou autogram!

192
00:15:10,287 --> 00:15:13,657
Autogram, g. Lockwood!
-Hou neto za uspomenu!

193
00:15:13,917 --> 00:15:15,542
I ja hou uspomenu!

194
00:15:15,794 --> 00:15:19,080
Hej, previe ste grubi!
Pocijepat ete me!

195
00:15:19,673 --> 00:15:22,210
Cos, uini neto!
Zovi mi taksi.

196
00:15:22,425 --> 00:15:23,541
Dobro, taksi.

197
00:15:24,219 --> 00:15:25,630
Ba ti hvala.

198
00:15:39,985 --> 00:15:41,611
Samo nastavite.
-Izlazite!

199
00:15:41,862 --> 00:15:44,567
Sve je u redu.
-Zvat u policiju!

200
00:15:44,782 --> 00:15:46,490
Samo nekoliko ulica.
-Ne dirajte me!

201
00:15:46,701 --> 00:15:48,907
Nisam kriminalac.
-Nije me briga!

202
00:15:49,162 --> 00:15:52,745
Jeste! Kriminalac ste! Vidjela sam
ve to lice. Vi ste gangster!

203
00:15:52,957 --> 00:15:56,492
Vidjela sam vau sliku na tjeralici,
ili moda u novinama.

204
00:15:56,711 --> 00:15:57,576
Policaje!

205
00:15:57,795 --> 00:16:01,709
Ovaj je upao u moj auto i...
-Pa to je Don Lockwood!

206
00:16:01,966 --> 00:16:04,672
Don Lockwood?
-Kako ste? Je li sve u redu?

207
00:16:04,928 --> 00:16:08,214
Da. Auto mi je u kvaru.
Opkolili su me sa svih strana.

208
00:16:08,474 --> 00:16:11,095
Ba ste sretnica. Sve je u redu?
-O, da.

209
00:16:11,310 --> 00:16:13,219
Mislim da je sve u redu.
Laku no.

210
00:16:13,478 --> 00:16:15,104
Laku no.

211
00:16:17,649 --> 00:16:20,521
Hvala to ste mi spasili ivot.
Sad u izai.

212
00:16:20,737 --> 00:16:23,653
Idem do Beverly Hillsa.
Da vas kamo povezem?

213
00:16:23,906 --> 00:16:28,402
Presvukao bih se. Ja sam na uglu
Sunseta i Camdena. Idete u tom pravcu?

214
00:16:28,619 --> 00:16:30,030
Da, idem.

215
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:37,085
Htio bih znati kome imam
zahvaliti na gostoprimstvu.

216
00:16:37,337 --> 00:16:39,081
Selden. Kathy Selden.

217
