Drago mi je.

218
00:16:41,591 --> 00:16:43,418
Oprostite to sam vas uplaio.

219
00:16:43,635 --> 00:16:46,885
Moji oboavatelji znaju
iskazati preveliku ljubav.

220
00:16:47,139 --> 00:16:49,808
Od njih ste, dakle, bjeali?

221
00:16:50,058 --> 00:16:53,013
Oni su vas ovako oerupali?
Strano!

222
00:16:56,232 --> 00:16:58,355
Da. Je, zar ne?

223
00:16:58,609 --> 00:17:00,103
Ba jest strano.

224
00:17:00,820 --> 00:17:03,572
Mi filmski glumci smo slavni...

225
00:17:03,781 --> 00:17:07,399
...ali katkad dobijemo i po glavi.
To moramo pretrpjeti.

226
00:17:07,911 --> 00:17:11,825
Ljudi misle da ivimo
raskono i romantino.

227
00:17:12,082 --> 00:17:13,909
U zbilji smo usamljeni.

228
00:17:15,167 --> 00:17:16,449
Vrlo usamljeni.

229
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:21,212
Oprostite to sam vas
smatrala kriminalcem.

230
00:17:21,466 --> 00:17:25,546
Ali pod ovakvim okolnostima...
Znala sam da sam vas negdje vidjela.

231
00:17:25,762 --> 00:17:28,218
Koji moj film ste gledali?

232
00:17:28,432 --> 00:17:29,511
Ne znam.

233
00:17:29,724 --> 00:17:31,516
Jedan sam va film gledala.

234
00:17:32,311 --> 00:17:35,062
Jedan?
-Mislim da ste se s nekim borili.

235
00:17:35,314 --> 00:17:37,271
Glumili ste s Linom Lamont.

236
00:17:37,524 --> 00:17:39,316
Ne idem esto u kino.

237
00:17:39,526 --> 00:17:42,611
Kad vidi jedan film,
vidio si ih sve.

238
00:17:43,906 --> 00:17:44,771
Ba vam hvala.

239
00:17:45,032 --> 00:17:46,195
Bez zamjerke.

240
00:17:46,450 --> 00:17:48,526
Filmovi su za zabavu masa.

241
00:17:48,786 --> 00:17:51,823
Oni na ekranu me ne mogu dirnuti.

242
00:17:52,081 --> 00:17:55,700
Ne govore, ne glume,
samo se previe krevelje.

243
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:57,371
Znate.

244
00:17:59,214 --> 00:18:00,127
Ovako.

245
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,832
Onako kao to ja radim?

246
00:18:03,593 --> 00:18:04,921
Da.

247
00:18:05,345 --> 00:18:08,097
Stigosmo.
Sunset i Camden.

248
00:18:09,934 --> 00:18:12,340
Znai, ja nisam glumac?

249
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:15,016
Pantomima nije gluma?
-Nikako.

250
00:18:15,272 --> 00:18:18,771
Glumiti znai imati sjajnu ulogu
i izgovarati uzviene rijei

251
00:18:18,984 --> 00:18:20,183
Shakespearea, Ibsena.

252
00:18:20,444 --> 00:18:22,317
ime se vi bavite u ivotu...

253
00:18:22,571 --> 00:18:25,858
...da se tako rugate
mojem skromnom pozivu?

254
00:18:26,076 --> 00:18:27,819
Ja sam kazalina glumica.

255
00:18:28,036 --> 00:18:29,578
O, kazalina glumica.

256
00:18:29,788 --> 00:18:32,195
Volio bih vas vidjeti.
Glumite li trenutno?

257
00:18:32,456 --> 00:18:35,660
Mogu proistiti svoj engleski
jezik ili povesti prevoditelja.

258
00:18:36,086 --> 00:18:37,746
Ako uope putaju
filmske glumce.

259
00:18:38,005 --> 00:18:40,839
Trenutano ne glumim nigdje.
Ali ii u u New York i...

260
00:18:41,049 --> 00:18:45,426
Oh, u New York! ut emo da ste
postali velika zvijezda, zar ne?

261
00:18:45,637 --> 00:18:49,006
Kathy Selden glumi Juliju,
Lady Macbeth, ili kralja Leara!

262
00:18:49,266 --> 00:18:50,641
Morat ete pustiti bradu!

263
00:18:50,892 --> 00:18:54,344
alite se vi, ali gluma u kazalitu
je dostojanstven zanat.

264
00:18:54,563 --> 00:18:56,472
Kako ste uobraeni!

265
00:18:56,732 --> 00:19:00,777
Vi ste samo sjena na ekranu,
nemate ni krvi i mesa.

266
00:19:00,986 --> 00:19:03,394
Stanite!
-to vam mogu ako sam samo sjena?

267
00:19:03,614 --> 00:19:07,529
Dalje ruke od mene!
To to ste filmska zvijezda...

268
00:19:07,785 --> 00:19:11,486
...ne znai da u se onesvijestiti
pred vama. Ne dirajte me!

269
00:19:11,706 --> 00:19:14,196
Ne plaite se, gospo.
Neu vam nauditi.

270
00:19:14,458 --> 00:19:19,417
Skromni sam lakrdija. A vi?
Nedostini ste mi.

271
00:19:19,922 --> 00:19:21,714
Poite s Bogom, gospo.

272
00:19:21,966 --> 00:19:25,052
A ja u se otrgnuti od vas.

273
00:19:37,108 --> 00:19:41,022
Je li ovo kua R.F. Simpsona?
Ja sam iz grupe kokos-djevojke.

274
00:19:41,279 --> 00:19:45,490
O, da. Nastupate tamo otraga.
-Vidim. Hvala.

275
00:20:08,682 --> 00:20:11,054
Zgodna zabavica.
-Hvala, Roscoe.

276
00:20:11,309 --> 00:20:14,311
G. Brown, zaista ete mi nai
ulogu u filmu?

277
00:20:14,563 --> 00:20:16,556
Mislim da hou.
-Zaista?

278
00:20:16,816 --> 00:20:20,434
Don! Film je sjajan.
-Uivali smo u tvom filmu.

279
00:20:20,737 --> 00:20:24,105
Zar si putovao preko Australije?
-Hej, Cos. Ispriavam se.

280
00:20:24,365 --> 00:20:27,235
Reci mi istinu.
Jesam li ja dobar glumac?

281
