-Bok, Don.

358
00:25:48,202 --> 00:25:49,946
'Jutro, momci.

359
00:25:50,204 --> 00:25:51,913
Jesi li itao Variety?

360
00:25:52,123 --> 00:25:55,871
"Prvi zvuni film Pjeva jazza postigao
