Evo je, g. Dexter.

441
00:31:08,202 --> 00:31:11,073
Konano! Dolazi nam naa
vodea dama.

442
00:31:11,288 --> 00:31:14,622
Ova vlasulja tei tonu.
Tko se tako oblaio?

443
00:31:14,834 --> 00:31:16,079
Svi u ono vrijeme.

444
00:31:16,294 --> 00:31:17,954
Tad su svi bili budale.

445
00:31:18,171 --> 00:31:20,045
Izgleda predivno, Lina.
-Izgleda sjajno.

446
00:31:20,256 --> 00:31:22,130
Dobro e pristajati sceni.

447
00:31:23,009 --> 00:31:23,839
Hvala, Joe.

448
00:31:24,052 --> 00:31:27,920
Traila sam te one veeri.
Gdje si bio?

449
00:31:28,140 --> 00:31:29,681
Imao sam posla.

450
00:31:29,933 --> 00:31:32,970
Znam kakvog si imao posla.
Traio si je.

451
00:31:33,186 --> 00:31:35,392
U stvari, jesam.
-Zato?

452
00:31:35,647 --> 00:31:36,893
Brinem zbog nje.

453
00:31:37,107 --> 00:31:39,064
Trebao bi brinuti o meni.

454
00:31:39,317 --> 00:31:42,189
Ja sam ona kojoj su u lice
bacili kremu od vanilije.

455
00:31:42,447 --> 00:31:44,854
Ali ti nisi ostala
bez posla, a ona jest.

456
00:31:45,073 --> 00:31:48,193
Nego to! Zato to
sam ja to potaknula.

457
00:31:48,411 --> 00:31:49,240
to?

458
00:31:49,453 --> 00:31:52,823
Nisu je htjeli otpustiti
pa sam to ja zatraila.

459
00:31:53,082 --> 00:31:54,743
Zato...
-Don, sjeti se!

460
00:31:54,959 --> 00:31:58,709
Ti si u nju ludo zaljubljen,
a ona je previe stidljiva.

461
00:31:59,172 --> 00:32:01,745
Cosmo, glazba ugoaja.

462
00:32:03,510 --> 00:32:04,885
Snimaj!

463
00:32:06,429 --> 00:32:07,840
Sad, Don.

464
00:32:08,098 --> 00:32:09,260
Ui.

465
00:32:10,517 --> 00:32:11,596
Sad si je opazio.

466
00:32:11,852 --> 00:32:13,429
Prilazi joj.

467
00:32:18,233 --> 00:32:21,982
Ti otrovna zmijo!
Nagovorila si ih da je najure.

468
00:32:22,196 --> 00:32:26,194
Kad je se samo doepam,
nee joj biti lako.

469
00:32:26,451 --> 00:32:28,822
Nikad nisam uo
neto tako podlo.

470
00:32:29,036 --> 00:32:30,494
Dobro. Sjajno izgleda.

471
00:32:31,331 --> 00:32:32,872
Zato si to uradila?

472
00:32:33,123 --> 00:32:36,161
Ona ti se svia.
Vidi se.

473
00:32:36,419 --> 00:32:37,878
Znai tako?

474
00:32:38,130 --> 00:32:42,341
Vjeruj mi, ne volim je upola
toliko koliko tebe mrzim.

475
00:32:42,592 --> 00:32:44,087
Gmazu!

476
00:32:44,344 --> 00:32:47,095
Slomit e moje bolno srce.

477
00:32:47,305 --> 00:32:49,381
Slomit u ti svaku kosku.

478
00:32:49,599 --> 00:32:51,889
Tko e ti pomoi, balvane?

479
00:32:52,477 --> 00:32:53,556
Sad je poljubi.

480
00:32:55,397 --> 00:32:56,228
Tako je.

481
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:57,270
Jo.

482
00:32:57,482 --> 00:32:58,312
Sjajno.

483
00:32:58,525 --> 00:32:59,770
Rez!

484
00:33:00,944 --> 00:33:05,108
Ljubi me s arom, pa nee mi
valjda rei da nita ne osjea!

485
00:33:05,324 --> 00:33:08,491
Ja sam najvei glumac svijeta.
Radije u poljubiti otrovnog pauka!

486
00:33:08,744 --> 00:33:10,618
Ne misli ozbiljno!
-Ne?

487
00:33:10,871 --> 00:33:13,078
Joe, donesi mi tarantulu.

488
00:33:13,291 --> 00:33:16,043
Ba ste kao dva golupia.
Snimit emo sljedeu scenu.

489
00:33:16,293 --> 00:33:17,290
Stani, Dexter!

490
00:33:17,921 --> 00:33:19,119
G. Simpson.

491
00:33:19,380 --> 00:33:20,626
Snimamo.

492
00:33:20,882 --> 00:33:23,124
Moete prekinuti snimanje.

493
00:33:23,343 --> 00:33:25,087
Svi! Prekinite!

494
00:33:25,303 --> 00:33:27,972
Prekidamo? Reci im da idu kui.
Snimanju je kraj.

495
00:33:28,180 --> 00:33:29,759
to eka? Reci im!

496
00:33:30,016 --> 00:33:32,589
Svi kui dok vam se
ne javimo! to je ovo?

497
00:33:32,811 --> 00:33:33,725
to se dogodilo?

498
00:33:33,937 --> 00:33:36,095
Pjeva jazza.
To se dogodilo.

499
00:33:36,314 --> 00:33:39,601
O, moja draga mamice
tamo kod Alabamice

500
00:33:39,819 --> 00:33:43,270
Nije vic. Film je senzacija.
Gledatelji vrite, trae jo takvih.

501
00:33:43,489 --> 00:33:45,814
ega?
-Zvunih filmova.

502
00:33:46,033 --> 00:33:49,201
Glupost.
-Takvu glupost moramo mi snimiti.

503
00:33:49,412 --> 00:33:52,745
Rekoh vam da je zvuni film problem,
ali nitko me ne slua.

504
00:33:52,957 --> 00:33:57,335
Snimamo Vitez koji voli dvoboje
i to e bit na zvuni film.

505
00:33:57,546 --> 00:33:59,288
Znai, ostajem bez posla.

506
00:33:59,506 --> 00:34:01,297
Mogu poeti patiti
i napisati simfoniju.

507
00:34:01,550 --> 00:34:04,219
Osnovat e glazbeni odjel.

508
00:34:04,469 --> 00:34:07,423
Hvala. Mogu prestati patiti
i napisati simfoniju.

509
00:34:07,639 --> 00:34:10,391
ekajte! Zvuni filmovi!
Trebate saekati...

510
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:12,926
Svi studiji prelaze
na zvuni film.

511
00:34:13,145 --> 00:34:15,682
Sva kina opremaju zvunom opremom.
Mi neemo zaostati.

512
00:34:15,939 --> 00:34:17,398
Nita ne znamo o tome.

513
00:34:17,607 --> 00:34:19,185
A to trebamo znati?

514
00:34:19,401 --> 00:34:22,521
Sve radimo kao i prije,
samo dodajmo dijaloge.

515
00:34:22,780 --> 00:34:24,654
Bit e to senzacija.

516
00:34:25,032 --> 00:34:27,949
"Lamont i Lockwood su progovorili!"

517
00:34:28,161 --> 00:34:31,281
Pa mi i sad govorimo.
Ne govore li svi?

518
00:34:37,544 --> 00:34:38,826
REVOLUCIJA U HOLLYWOODU

519
00:34:39,713 --> 00:34:41,338
SVI SNIMAJU ZVUNE FILMOVE

520
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:43,916
SVI OBOAVAJU MUZIKE FILMOVE

521
00:34:48,682 --> 00:34:50,473
Imam osjeaj
da se ludira

522
00:34:50,684 --> 00:34:52,391
Imam osjeaj
da se zabavlja

523
00:34:52,645 --> 00:34:55,479
Brzo e me se rijeiti
kad se zavri zabava

524
00:34:55,689 --> 00:34:58,524
Danas je praznik,
vjenanje naslikane lutke

525
00:34:59,359 --> 00:35:01,068
Sretan dan,
vijest se iri...

526
00:35:01,278 --> 00:35:05,110
Da li da otkrijem
kako se doista osjeam?

527
00:35:05,366 --> 00:35:07,157
Da li da priznam?

528
00:35:09,412 --> 00:35:12,199
Imam osjeaj da se ludira
Imam osjeaj...

529
00:35:13,916 --> 00:35:15,411
Danas je praznik, danas...

530
00:35:15,626 --> 00:35:17,169
Da li da otkrijem

531
00:35:17,420 --> 00:35:18,997
Kako se doista osjeam?

532
00:35:30,975 --> 00:35:34,511
Prelijepa djevojko,
ti si najljepa slika

533
00:35:34,772 --> 00:35:38,223
Prelijepa djevojko,
ti si divna mjeavina

534
00:35:38,484 --> 00:35:43,110
Svega to lei
pod plavim nebom

535
00:35:44,073 --> 00:35:45,614
Moje srce plae

536
00:35:45,825 --> 00:35:47,616
Tko je to?
Ona zdesna ini mi se poznata.

537
00:35:49,745 --> 00:35:52,237
Igrala je za mene
u nekoliko programa.

538
00:35:52,457 --> 00:35:53,535
Vidio sam je ve.

539
00:35:53,749 --> 00:35:55,493
Bila bi dobra
kao Zeldina sestra.

540
00:35:55,709 --> 00:35:58,249
Dobra ideja.
-Oprostite.

541
00:35:59,505 --> 00:36:04,299
Bila plavua ili brineta
teko im je odoljeti

542
00:36:04,511 --> 00:36:07,381
Ljepa si od kraljice

543
00:36:08,474 --> 00:36:11,842
Usne su ti kao
stvorene za ljubljenje

544
00:36:12,102 --> 00:36:14,771
Tek ti je 16 ljeta

545
00:36:16,148 --> 00:36:19,731
Prelijepa djevojko,
ti si predivno stvorenje

546
00:36:19,943 --> 00:36:23,478
Prelijepa djevojko,
daj da pozovem sveenika

547
00:36:23,739 --> 00:36:25,483
to drugo mogu

548
00:36:25,741 --> 00:36:29,656
Nego da ti darujem
svoje srce?

549
00:36:31,622 --> 00:36:36,248
Prelijepa djevojka,
ona je kao umjetniko djelo

550
00:36:36,502 --> 00:36:39,457
Ima stila,
njena je kao svila

551
00:36:40,422 --> 00:36:44,551
Ali isto tako
ima dara

552
00:36:46,971 --> 00:36:49,594
Za vrljanje po kui

553
00:36:49,850 --> 00:36:52,803
Je ova pidama

554
00:36:54,021 --> 00:36:56,974
Kaput joj je ukraen krznom

555
00:36:57,232 --> 00:36:59,474
Da se povea dramatinost

556
00:37:00,986 --> 00:37:02,480
Je li tko za tenis?

557
00:37:02,696 --> 00:37:05,650
Moda je ovako lake igrati

558
00:37:07,368 --> 00:37:09,407
Obara ih s nogu

559
00:37:09,662 --> 00:37:13,031
Takvom veernjom haljinom

560
00:37:14,458 --> 00:37:19,286
Ne moe biti tako skromna
na plai ni kraj bazena

561
00:37:20,798 --> 00:37:23,586
A za ljeto, organdi

562
00:37:23,842 --> 00:37:26,595
Koji te hladi

563
00:37:27,723 --> 00:37:30,047
Koliko odobravanja

564
00:37:30,309 --> 00:37:33,559
Za ovaj smjeli eir

565
00:37:34,145 --> 00:37:37,846
Ne moe ni sanjati
to sve moe sakriti

566
00:37:38,107 --> 00:37:40,396
U tim rukavima

567
00:37:40,736 --> 00:37:43,820
Biserna ogrlica uz
kostim od tvida

568
00:37:44,072 --> 00:37:46,695
Pravi je vrisak

569
00:37:47,618 --> 00:37:50,453
Za operu je obvezna lisica

570
00:37:50,662 --> 00:37:53,996
Gospa Dama kae: "Oboji ju!"

571
00:37:54,500 --> 00:37:57,170
Crnina je najbolja za sudnicu

572
00:37:57,421 --> 00:38:01,419
Impresionirat e suca

573
00:38:01,883 --> 00:38:06,296
Ali bjelina je prava boja
za vjenanje

574
00:38:06,554 --> 00:38:11,679
I ti eli biti
prikladno odjevena

575
00:38:14,020 --> 00:38:16,346
Prelijepa djevojko

576
00:38:17,649 --> 00:38:20,271
Ti si meni sve

577
00:38:20,527 --> 00:38:22,935
Predivna djevojko

578
00:38:24,198 --> 00:38:26,950
Ti si moja kraljica mode

579
00:38:27,159 --> 00:38:29,484
U ljubavnom sam vrtlogu...

580
00:38:31,496 --> 00:38:32,778
...zbog...

581
00:38:33,290 --> 00:38:38,416
...moje prelijepe djevojke!

582
00:38:47,680 --> 00:38:49,507
Izvanredno!
-Hvala.

583
00:38:49,724 --> 00:38:50,555
Kathy, doi!

584
00:38:50,768 --> 00:38:53,056
Bit e to poetak
novog filmskog anra.

585
00:38:53,269 --> 00:38:56,307
Ovo je g. Simpson.
eli da igra Zeldinu sestru.

586
00:38:56,524 --> 00:38:57,803
Sjajno!

587
00:38:58,024 --> 00:38:59,269
Hej, Kathy!

588
00:38:59,568 --> 00:39:00,849
Ovo je Kathy Selden.

589
00:39:01,111 --> 00:39:02,606
Hvala na ponudi.
Lijepo od vas.

590
00:39:02,864 --> 00:39:04,738
ekajte!
-Ne, u redu je.

591
00:39:04,948 --> 00:39:07,866
Prije nego vas g. Lockwood
podsjeti, rei u vam da sam ja ona...

592
00:39:08,118 --> 00:39:13,077
...koja je bacila tortu na gicu Lamont,
a bila je namijenjena g. Lockwoodu.

593
00:39:13,332 --> 00:39:15,372
ao mi je. Trebala sam vam rei.

594
00:39:15,585 --> 00:39:17,661
ekajte. O emu se radi?

595
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:21,206
Uposlili bismo gicu Selden, ali ako se
ti i Lina ne biste sloili s time...

596
00:39:21,466 --> 00:39:23,174
Zato? Pa to bi bilo sjajno!

597
00:39:23,426 --> 00:39:24,919
Traimo je tjednima.

598
00:39:25,178 --> 00:39:26,672
Govori li i u Linino ime?

599
00:39:26,887 --> 00:39:29,925
U firmi Coconut Groove
mogu raditi to im Lina kae.

600
00:39:30,142 --> 00:39:32,928
Ali vi ste glavni u studiju.
-Da, glavni sam.

601
00:39:33,145 --> 00:39:35,932
Angairajte je.
Samo Lini ni rijei.

602
00:39:36,148 --> 00:39:37,012
Pobrini se za to.

603
00:39:37,274 --> 00:39:38,306
Hvala vam, g. Simpson!

604
00:39:38,567 --> 00:39:42,316
Drago mi je to smo te nali.
Pretraili smo sve torte u gradu.

605
00:39:43,990 --> 00:39:46,066
Nije vam neugodno
da vas vide u mom drutvu?

606
00:39:46,284 --> 00:39:48,952
Mislite, veliku umjetnicu sa
skromnim lakrdijaem?

607
00:39:49,202 --> 00:39:53,497
Ne ba. Ali zar obino
ne ruate fazana s gicom Lamont?

608
00:39:53,708 --> 00:39:57,789
uj, Kathy. Sve to o Lini i meni
samo je propaganda.

609
00:39:58,046 --> 00:40:00,583
Moda i vie od toga...

610
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:05,169
...sudei po onom to sam itala
u asopisima za vae oboavatelje.

611
00:40:05,470 --> 00:40:08,803
itate takve asopise?

612
00:40:09,057 --> 00:40:12,261
Vidjela sam ih kod frizera
ili u zubarskom uredu...

613
00:40:12,477 --> 00:40:14,138
...kao i svaka ena.

614
00:40:14,354 --> 00:40:15,599
Ozbiljno?

615
00:40:17,524 --> 00:40:18,983
Kupujem 4 do 5 asopisa
mjeseno.

616
00:40:19,234 --> 00:40:21,227
Kupujete 4 do 5...?

617
00:40:22,029 --> 00:40:23,938
Da se vratimo na bitno.

618
00:40:24,197 --> 00:40:27,069
Vi i gica Lina ste
intimni u svim filmovima?

619
00:40:27,284 --> 00:40:29,989
Jeste li gledali sve
moje filmove?

620
00:40:32,372 --> 00:40:35,244
Ne, ali ako razmislim,
vidjela sam 8 ili 9.

621
00:40:35,501 --> 00:40:36,496
8 ili 9?

622
00:40:36,753 --> 00:40:39,422
ini mi se da netko ree:

623
00:40:39,673 --> 00:40:42,923
"Kad vidi jedan,
vidio si ih sve."

624
00:40:44,635 --> 00:40:47,721
One veeri izgovorila sam
strane stvari, zar ne?

625
00:40:48,181 --> 00:40:50,636
Zasluio sam ih.

626
00:40:50,850 --> 00:40:54,385
Naravno, moram priznati,
bio sam vrlo razoaran.

627
00:40:54,979 --> 00:41:00,021
Tako razoaran, da
otad mislim samo na vas.

628
00:41:00,944 --> 00:41:02,189
Ozbiljno?

629
00:41:03,573 --> 00:41:04,817
Ozbiljno.

630
00:41:07,951 --> 00:41:09,411
I ja sam bila razoarana.

631
00:41:11,163 --> 00:41:12,990
Kathy!

632
00:41:13,249 --> 00:41:15,870
Sad kad sam vas opet sreo...

633
00:41:19,797 --> 00:41:22,751
Pokuavam vam neto objasniti,
ali sam...

634
00:41:23,009 --> 00:41:24,634
Tako sam zbunjen.

635
00:41:24,844 --> 00:41:27,595
Ne mogu sroiti nita
ako okolina nije prava.

636
00:41:27,805 --> 00:41:28,755
to hoete rei?

637
00:41:31,600 --> 00:41:32,977
Doite ovamo.

638
00:41:41,362 --> 00:41:43,401
Ovo je prava okolina.

639
00:41:44,657 --> 00:41:46,317
To je prazna pozornica.

640
00:41:46,576 --> 00:41:48,117
Samo na prvi pogled.

641
00:41:48,369 --> 00:41:49,862
Ali ekajte malo.

642
00:41:51,830 --> 00:41:54,037
Divan zalaz sunca.

643
00:41:57,128 --> 00:41:59,879
Maglica s dalekih breuljaka.

644
00:42:02,008 --> 00:42:04,250
Obojena svjetlost iz vrta.

645
00:42:06,638 --> 00:42:11,549
Djevojka stoji na balkonu
a oko nje svuda su rue.

646
00:42:15,397 --> 00:42:17,224
Osvijetljena je mjeseinom.

647
00:42:17,482 --> 00:42:20,852
Dodat emo 555.555 kW
zvjezdane praine.

648
00:42:24,239 --> 00:42:26,565
Lagani ljetni vjetri.

649
00:42:30,121 --> 00:42:32,576
Zaista si predivna pod
mjeseinom, Kathy.

650
00:42:34,167 --> 00:42:38,034
Sad kad si u pravoj okolini,
moe li se izjasniti?

651
00:42:40,382 --> 00:42:41,211
Pokuat u.

652
00:42:42,801 --> 00:42:45,469
ivot je bio pjesma

653
00:42:45,971 --> 00:42:48,806
Tad si se ti pojavila

654
00:42:49,056 --> 00:42:54,183
Bio bih budan
i leao cijelu no

655
00:42:55,647 --> 00:42:57,973
Kad bih samo znao

656
00:42:58,858 --> 00:43:01,184
Da je i tebi stalo do mene

657
00:43:01,903 --> 00:43:03,730
Samo da znam

658
00:43:04,198 --> 00:43:08,362
Rekao bih ti ja:

659
00:43:11,205 --> 00:43:15,784
Ti si mi suena

660
00:43:19,380 --> 00:43:24,007
Ja sam tebi suen

661
00:43:27,514 --> 00:43:30,764
Priroda te je nainila
po savrenom uzorku

662
00:43:31,226 --> 00:43:34,346
I kad je zavrila stvaranje

663
00:43:35,564 --> 00:43:39,265
Ti si postala sve najslae

664
00:43:40,277 --> 00:43:43,113
Umotano u jedno

665
00:43:43,531 --> 00:43:45,191
Ti si kao

666
00:43:45,408 --> 00:43:50,365
Jednostavna melodija

667
00:43:53,416 --> 00:43:58,540
Koja mi nikad ne izlazi
iz glave

668
00:44:01,758 --> 00:44:04,961
Sretan sam

669
00:44:05,888 --> 00:44:09,672
Jer su aneli poslali tebe

670
00:44:10,642 --> 00:44:14,260
Namijenili su te

671
00:44:15,480 --> 00:44:18,600
Ba meni

672
00:45:45,532 --> 00:45:48,736
Sretan sam

673
00:45:50,830 --> 00:45:54,958
