Naa e ljubav trajati sve dok
se zvijezde ne ugase.

1159
01:29:20,089 --> 01:29:22,046
Sad ti, Kathy.

1160
01:29:22,967 --> 01:29:25,293
Nita nas ne moe razdvojiti.

1161
01:29:25,553 --> 01:29:29,385
Naa e ljubav trajati sve dok
se zvijezde ne ugase.

1162
01:29:29,766 --> 01:29:31,723
Sjajno, savreno! Rez!

1163
01:29:34,229 --> 01:29:37,064
Sve dok se zvijezde ne ugase.

1164
01:29:37,691 --> 01:29:39,767
Kathy, ja te volim.

1165
01:29:41,945 --> 01:29:44,187
Jedva ekam da
dovrimo film.

1166
01:29:44,448 --> 01:29:47,817
Nema vie tajni.
Reu u sve Lini i svima.

1167
01:29:48,077 --> 01:29:50,615
Tvoji e oboavatelji
biti razoarani.

1168
01:29:50,830 --> 01:29:54,578
Vana mi je samo
jedna oboavateljica.

1169
01:29:58,129 --> 01:29:58,994
Evo!

1170
01:29:59,212 --> 01:30:02,298
to sam ti rekla!
-Hvala, Zelda. Prava si prijateljica.

1171
01:30:02,509 --> 01:30:06,459
Smjesta izbacite ovu djevojku.
Nee ona biti moj glas.

1172
01:30:06,680 --> 01:30:08,257
Zelda mi je sve rekla.

1173
01:30:08,515 --> 01:30:11,301
Hvala ti. Ba si prava prijateljica.
-Svakako, Don.

1174
01:30:11,559 --> 01:30:12,758
ujte, Don nije...

1175
01:30:13,019 --> 01:30:15,688
Don?! Kako se usuuje
zvati ga Don?

1176
01:30:15,938 --> 01:30:18,939
Zvala sam ga Don prije
nego si se rodila.

1177
01:30:19,150 --> 01:30:20,894
Ovaj...
Ljubila si ga!

1178
01:30:21,152 --> 01:30:24,604
Ja sam ljubio nju.
Jer je volim.

1179
01:30:24,823 --> 01:30:29,615
Pa to je smijeno. Svi znaju
da voli samo mene.

1180
01:30:30,037 --> 01:30:33,157
Sluaj me, Lina.
Pokuaj shvatiti.

1181
01:30:33,373 --> 01:30:35,082
Njom u se oeniti.

1182
01:30:35,334 --> 01:30:38,003
Ludice. Nije ona taj tip.

1183
01:30:38,254 --> 01:30:41,089
Ona koketira s tobom
da te iskoristi.

1184
01:30:41,299 --> 01:30:45,676
Sprijeit u to.
Idem odmah Simpsonu.

1185
01:30:45,887 --> 01:30:47,381
Prekasno. Film je gotov.

1186
01:30:47,597 --> 01:30:49,886
Da nije te djevojke,
i ti bi bila gotova.

1187
01:30:50,141 --> 01:30:53,094
Koliko ja znam,
jedino je ona gotova.

1188
01:30:53,353 --> 01:30:54,349
Tko e ikad uti za nju?

1189
01:30:54,603 --> 01:30:57,771
Svi. Misli da Zelda
tebi pomae iz ljubavi?

1190
01:30:57,983 --> 01:30:59,857
Kathy joj je gotovo ukrala film.

1191
01:31:00,068 --> 01:31:01,978
Ona ti je samo uinila uslugu.

1192
01:31:02,237 --> 01:31:05,273
Dobit e priznanje za glumu.

1193
01:31:05,532 --> 01:31:09,232
Objavit ete da ja sama ne
govorim i ne pjevam?

1194
01:31:09,452 --> 01:31:11,326
Nego to? to si mislila?

1195
01:31:11,580 --> 01:31:13,619
To ne smiju.
-Ve je sve spremno.

1196
01:31:13,875 --> 01:31:16,164
Predvidjeli su cijelu
propagandnu kampanju.

1197
01:31:16,418 --> 01:31:17,829
Kampanju?

1198
01:31:18,087 --> 01:31:19,914
Ne mogu od Line
napraviti budalu!

1199
01:31:20,173 --> 01:31:22,794
Ne mogu Linu Lamont
izvri ruglu.

1200
01:31:23,050 --> 01:31:25,968
to oni misle, da sam glupa
ili slino?

1201
01:31:26,220 --> 01:31:28,509
Ja donosim veu zaradu...

1202
01:31:29,307 --> 01:31:31,181
...nego Calvin Coolidge...

1203
01:31:31,392 --> 01:31:33,219
...zajedno!

1204
01:31:35,313 --> 01:31:40,022
"Monumantal Pictures je zadivljen
pjevanjem i plesanjem Line Lamont."

1205
01:31:40,234 --> 01:31:41,184
Nikad to nisam izjavio.

1206
01:31:41,445 --> 01:31:45,489
"Lina Lamont e veeras pokazati
svoj veliki talenat za pjevanje."

1207
01:31:45,699 --> 01:31:48,819
To e pokvariti raune
naoj propagandi.

1208
01:31:49,036 --> 01:31:51,159
Sve je spremno za
promoviranje Kathy Selden.

1209
01:31:51,372 --> 01:31:53,448
A sad ovo.
Mogao si nam javiti.

1210
01:31:53,666 --> 01:31:56,417
Nisam znao za ovo.
Nemam s tim veze.

1211
01:31:56,668 --> 01:31:57,867
to sad moemo?

1212
01:31:58,128 --> 01:31:59,078
Nita.

1213
01:32:00,088 --> 01:32:02,662
Ba nita.

1214
01:32:02,926 --> 01:32:06,009
Nee valjda rei novinarima
da je Lina Lamont...

1215
01:32:06,220 --> 01:32:08,509
...velika laljivka, zar ne?

1216
01:32:08,764 --> 01:32:10,342
Ti si ovo zakuhala?

1217
01:32:10,599 --> 01:32:13,933
Dala sam ekskluzivnu priu
svim novinama u gradu.

1218
01:32:14,186 --> 01:32:16,310
Nee ti to upaliti.
Rod, pozovi novinare.

1219
01:32:16,564 --> 01:32:18,307
Ne bih to da sam na tvom mjestu.

1220
01:32:18,566 --> 01:32:20,606
Nee ti meni zapovijedati.

1221
01:32:20,860 --> 01:32:24,312
to misli tko sam?
Da sam glupa ili slino?

1222
01:32:24,572 --> 01:32:27,657
Rekla sam svom odvjetniku
da proui ugovor.

1223
01:32:27,909 --> 01:32:29,024
Ugovor?

1224
01:32:29,286 --> 01:32:32,489
Svoju propagandu vodim ja,
a ne ti.

1225
01:32:32,706 --> 01:32:36,407
Studio je odgovoran za sve
to se pie o meni.

1226
01:32:36,627 --> 01:32:39,746
Ako mi se ne svia,
mogu vas tuakati.

1227
01:32:40,005 --> 01:32:41,085
to?

1228
01:32:41,298 --> 01:32:43,539
Tuakati.

1229
01:32:43,758 --> 01:32:46,677
Ako im kae o Kathy Selden...

1230
01:32:46,929 --> 01:32:51,638
...bit e to "kodljivo i pogubno"
za moju karijeru.

1231
01:32:52,310 --> 01:32:55,429
Tuit u te i
izgubit e cijeli studio.

1232
01:32:55,688 --> 01:32:57,930
Glupost.
-Tako pie.

1233
01:32:58,190 --> 01:32:59,601
Evo ovdje.

1234
01:32:59,859 --> 01:33:04,356
Sve stoji u ugovoru od
58.56.1925., paragraf 34, slovo A.

1235
01:33:04,573 --> 01:33:06,613
"Prva stranka ugovora..."

1236
01:33:06,825 --> 01:33:08,652
To sam ja.
-Pobijedila si, Lina.

1237
01:33:08,869 --> 01:33:11,490
Skinut emo Kathyno ime
s ekrana.

1238
01:33:11,705 --> 01:33:13,034
U redu, uinite to.

1239
01:33:13,290 --> 01:33:15,448
Zavrite ve jednom s tim.

1240
01:33:15,709 --> 01:33:17,085
Zadovoljna?

1241
01:33:17,294 --> 01:33:19,785
Ima jo neto.

1242
01:33:20,214 --> 01:33:24,294
Hoe da promijenim ime studija
u Lamont Pictures?

1243
01:33:24,552 --> 01:33:26,509
Ba zgodno.

1244
01:33:26,762 --> 01:33:28,554
Mislila sam neto drugo.

1245
01:33:28,806 --> 01:33:31,297
Dao si toj djevojici malu ulogu
u Zeldinom filmu...

1246
01:33:31,559 --> 01:33:34,097
...i obeao si joj
jo veu u iduem.

1247
01:33:34,354 --> 01:33:35,848
Pa to?

1248
01:33:36,064 --> 01:33:38,816
Budui da je bila tako
sjajna u dubliranju mog glasa...

1249
01:33:39,066 --> 01:33:42,353
...zar ne misli da bi trebala
da radi samo to?

1250
01:33:42,612 --> 01:33:44,854
I nita drugo.
-Poludjela si.

1251
01:33:45,114 --> 01:33:48,152
Jo sam uvijek vanija
za ovaj studio od nje.

1252
01:33:48,368 --> 01:33:50,160
Ne bih to uradio ni za to.

1253
01:33:50,371 --> 01:33:53,870
Unitilo bi joj karijeru.
Ljudi ne rade takve stvari.

1254
01:33:54,083 --> 01:33:55,661
Ljudi?

1255
01:33:55,960 --> 01:33:57,787
Ja nisam ljudi.

1256
01:33:58,045 --> 01:33:59,837
Ja sam...

1257
01:34:03,216 --> 01:34:07,594
"Blistava, svjetlucava zvijezda
na nebu filma."

1258
01:34:07,805 --> 01:34:09,632
Tako pie...

1259
01:34:09,933 --> 01:34:11,307
...ovdje.

1260
01:34:15,479 --> 01:34:16,310
VEERAS PREMIJERA

1261
01:34:16,814 --> 01:34:19,056
ZVUNI FILM S PJEVANJEM

1262
01:34:19,317 --> 01:34:22,104
DON LOCKWOOD I LINA LAMONT
"VITEZ KOJI PLEE"

1263
01:34:23,780 --> 01:34:28,608
Oh, Pierre, duo.
Napokon sam te nala.

1264
01:34:30,078 --> 01:34:33,862
Pierre, ti si ranjen!
Reci neto.

1265
01:34:34,708 --> 01:34:38,706
Poljubio bih je strasno

1266
01:34:39,463 --> 01:34:41,255
A ti?

1267
01:34:41,590 --> 01:34:43,417
A ti?

1268
01:34:43,926 --> 01:34:47,758
A da sam ta djevojka ja?

1269
01:34:48,056 --> 01:34:49,598
Bi li me poljubio?

1270
01:34:50,183 --> 01:34:52,222
Bi li me poljubio?

1271
01:34:52,684 --> 01:34:55,936
Pierre, grli me u beskraj!

1272
01:34:56,189 --> 01:34:57,434
Lockwood je senzacionalan.

1273
01:34:57,691 --> 01:35:01,356
Da, ali Lamontova!
Ima sjajan glas.

1274
01:35:01,612 --> 01:35:04,103
Uspjelo je, zar ne?

1275
01:35:04,322 --> 01:35:08,651
Naa e ljubav trajati
dok se zvijezde ne ugase.

1276
01:35:09,328 --> 01:35:13,990
Bi li se usudila rei:

1277
01:35:14,207 --> 01:35:19,332
Uinimo isto to i oni?

1278
01:35:20,798 --> 01:35:25,757
Ja bih

1279
01:35:26,053 --> 01:35:30,181
A ti?

1280
01:35:40,944 --> 01:35:43,352
SVRETAK

1281
01:35:53,998 --> 01:35:55,375
Velik uspjeh.

1282
01:35:55,584 --> 01:35:58,288
estitam. Da nije bilo vas...
-Hvala.

1283
01:35:58,504 --> 01:36:00,412
Kathy, uspjeli smo!
-udesno!

1284
01:36:00,673 --> 01:36:02,464
Don, bilo je sjajno!

1285
01:36:02,675 --> 01:36:05,593
Bila si dobra, Lina.
Pjeva kao Kathy Selden.

1286
01:36:05,802 --> 01:36:08,721
I dugo u biti dobra.

1287
01:36:08,932 --> 01:36:09,880
Kako to?

1288
01:36:10,140 --> 01:36:13,427
I dalje e ona pjevati
umjesto mene.

1289
01:36:13,686 --> 01:36:14,801
Lina!

1290
01:36:15,063 --> 01:36:18,728
Znao sam da se neto kuha
u toj atiranoj glavi.

1291
01:36:18,984 --> 01:36:22,103
Kathy ima svoju karijeru.
Ovo je bilo samo za jedan film.

1292
01:36:22,362 --> 01:36:23,737
To ti misli.

1293
01:36:23,988 --> 01:36:25,613
Ma daj!

1294
01:36:25,865 --> 01:36:27,490
Malo je pretjerala, zar ne?

1295
01:36:28,368 --> 01:36:29,779
Sluaj, ti zmijo!

1296
01:36:30,036 --> 01:36:32,824
Nemoj se zanositi budunou.
Reci joj.

1297
01:36:33,081 --> 01:36:35,454
Sluajte, ovaj pljesak
je za mene.

1298
01:36:35,709 --> 01:36:37,334
Dolazi nam velika lova.

1299
01:36:37,544 --> 01:36:41,494
Neete sve odbaciti zbog
neke nepoznate djevojice.

1300
01:36:41,757 --> 01:36:43,666
To je zlatni rudnik!

1301
01:36:43,926 --> 01:36:46,049
Mogu li ja neto rei?

1302
01:36:46,304 --> 01:36:47,548
Ja to neu vie raditi.

1303
01:36:47,805 --> 01:36:51,387
Ima petogodinji ugovor
pa e morati.

1304
01:36:51,642 --> 01:36:54,098
to je?
Zato je ne otjera?

1305
01:36:54,354 --> 01:36:56,181
Ne znam, zbunjen sam.

1306
01:36:56,439 --> 01:36:59,642
Publika je poludjela!
-Idite se pokloniti.

1307
01:36:59,859 --> 01:37:02,102
Simpsone, jednom sam vam dao
cigaru. Mogu li je dobiti natrag?

1308
01:37:02,321 --> 01:37:05,653
To je kao lavina.
Kathy, nema izbora.

1309
01:37:05,907 --> 01:37:09,110
Ako doe do tog,
nai novog momka. Meni je dosta.

1310
01:37:09,369 --> 01:37:12,739
Tko te treba? Ljudi e gledati moje
filmove pa glumila ja i s majmunom.

1311
01:37:12,999 --> 01:37:14,327
Don je sjajan.

1312
01:37:14,584 --> 01:37:17,121
Imam i ja tu neto rei.
Jo uvijek upravljam studijom.

1313
01:37:17,377 --> 01:37:18,789
Nemoj biti tako siguran.

1314
01:37:19,046 --> 01:37:22,331
Uvijek si svima upravljao,
i mnome.

1315
01:37:22,550 --> 01:37:26,001
Ali odsad ja upravljam.

1316
01:37:26,262 --> 01:37:28,504
Lamont Pictures, je li?

1317
01:37:28,765 --> 01:37:30,472
Pretjerala si.

1318
01:37:30,726 --> 01:37:33,013
Publika trai da neto kaete.
-Govor?

1319
01:37:33,269 --> 01:37:36,104
Svi su uvijek govorili
umjesto mene.

1320
01:37:36,356 --> 01:37:40,685
Ali veeras u sama.
Odrat u govor.

1321
01:37:40,944 --> 01:37:43,861
Ne, molim te!
-ekaj. ekaj.

1322
01:37:44,114 --> 01:37:47,981
Ovo je njezina velika no.
Ima pravo da govori.

1323
01:37:49,244 --> 01:37:51,533
Je li tako?
-Tako je.

1324
01:37:56,418 --> 01:37:58,458
Dame i gospodo.

1325
01:37:58,712 --> 01:37:59,744
Ne mogu vam rei...

1326
01:37:59,964 --> 01:38:02,122
...kako smo uzbueni zbog tako...

1327
01:38:02,341 --> 01:38:06,386
...toplog prijema naeg
prvog muzikog filma.

1328
01:38:06,637 --> 01:38:10,931
Ako smo vas malo zabavili,
unijeli radost u vae sive ivote...

1329
01:38:11,183 --> 01:38:13,425
...uinili da se osjetite bolje...

1330
01:38:13,687 --> 01:38:16,142
...bit emo sretni.

1331
01:38:17,273 --> 01:38:18,981
Budite blagoslovljeni!

1332
01:38:19,192 --> 01:38:20,935
Njezin glas nije bio
takav u filmu.

1333
01:38:21,194 --> 01:38:22,771
Prekini priu, Lina.
Pjevaj!

1334
01:38:30,412 --> 01:38:32,073
Imam ideju!

1335
01:38:32,456 --> 01:38:33,286
uj!

1336
01:38:37,419 --> 01:38:39,495
to u sad?

1337
01:38:39,755 --> 01:38:42,673
Bila si savrena.
Postavi mikrofon iza zastora.

1338
01:38:42,925 --> 01:38:46,210
Kathy e biti iza zastora
i pjevat e umjesto tebe.

1339
01:38:46,470 --> 01:38:49,922
Znai, ja u zijevati
a ona e pjevati?

1340
01:38:50,141 --> 01:38:51,801
Kao u filmu?
-Da.

1341
01:38:52,060 --> 01:38:53,887
Mora pjevati, Kathy.

1342
01:38:54,144 --> 01:38:58,060
Naravno, pjevat e, ima petogodinji
ugovor. Daj mikrofon!

1343
01:38:58,315 --> 01:39:00,557
Naprijed, Kathy.

1344
01:39:00,861 --> 01:39:02,023
Pjevat u.

1345
01:39:02,278 --> 01:39:04,105
Ali vie mi ne dolazi na oi!

1346
01:39:04,363 --> 01:39:06,237
Nikad vie!

1347
01:39:06,449 --> 01:39:08,073
Hajde, Lina.

1348
01:39:12,664 --> 01:39:14,372
to ete pjevati?

1349
01:39:18,336 --> 01:39:19,369
"Pjevajmo na kii."

1350
01:39:20,756 --> 01:39:22,001
"Pjevajmo na kii."

1351
01:39:24,426 --> 01:39:25,542
U kojem tonalitetu?

1352
01:39:28,472 --> 01:39:29,801
E-mol.

1353
01:39:30,015 --> 01:39:31,047
E-mol.

1354
01:39:44,531 --> 01:39:49,526
Pjevam na kii
Samo pjevam na kii

1355
01:39:49,744 --> 01:39:54,621
Kakav divan osjeaj
Ponovno sam sretan

1356
01:39:54,833 --> 01:39:59,874
Smjekam se oblacima
Oni su visoko, i tamni su

1357
01:40:00,088 --> 01:40:02,960
A meni je sunce u srcu

1358
01:40:03,176 --> 01:40:05,049
Oekujem ljubav

1359
01:40:05,303 --> 01:40:07,508
Oblaci rastjeruju sve

1360
01:40:07,763 --> 01:40:10,337
Sve ljude odavde

1361
01:40:10,558 --> 01:40:15,552
Ja sam na kii
A smijeak mi na licu

1362
01:40:15,813 --> 01:40:20,642
Koraam plonikom
I pjevam sretni refren

1363
01:40:20,903 --> 01:40:23,689
Samo pjevam
Pjevam na kii

1364
01:40:50,975 --> 01:40:52,304
Zaustavite onu djevojku!

1365
01:40:52,518 --> 01:40:54,476
Djevojku koja tri!

1366
01:40:54,729 --> 01:40:57,350
To je djevojka iji glas
ste veeras uli na filmu.

1367
01:40:57,565 --> 01:41:00,602
Ona je prava zvijezda ovog
filma: Kathy Selden!

1368
01:41:09,870 --> 01:41:13,072
Ti si...

1369
01:41:13,665 --> 01:41:17,710
...moja sretna zvijezda

1370
01:41:18,713 --> 01:41:21,167
Vidio sam te...

1371
01:41:21,381 --> 01:41:25,593
...ve izdaleka

1372
01:41:27,429 --> 01:41:32,556
Tvoje predivne oi
u mene su gledale

1373
01:41:34,979 --> 01:41:37,601
Sjale su

1374
01:41:39,150 --> 01:41:44,275
Bila sam opinjena

1375
01:41:44,948 --> 01:41:48,697
Ti si meni sve

1376
01:41:48,910 --> 01:41:52,991
Sve najsretnije

1377
01:41:53,540 --> 01:41:57,585
Sretna sam...

1378
01:41:57,795 --> 01:42:01,923
...u tvom zagrljaju

1379
01:42:02,716 --> 01:42:06,630
Ti si stvorila nebo

1380
01:42:06,887 --> 01:42:12,013
Na zemlji za mene

1381
01:42:13,895 --> 01:42:16,267
Ti si...

1382
01:42:16,522 --> 01:42:19,227
...moja...

1383
